        <ab>HERE IN THE RESTING PLACE</ab>
        <ab>SHE HAD CHOSEN LIE THE RE</ab>
        <ab>MAINS OF ELIZABETH SUSAN</ab>
        <ab>PERCY DAUGHTER OF ALGERNON</ab>
        <ab>EARL OF BEVERLEY BORN DEC.29</ab>
        <ab>1782 WHO DIED AT ROME SUDDENLY</ab>
        <ab>BUT NOT UNPREPARED AP 7. 1847 BE</ab>
        <ab>LOVED &amp; RESPECTED BY ALL FOR HER</ab>
        <ab>GENTLE MANNERS CULTIVATED</ab>
        <ab>TASTE CHEERFUL CHRISTIAN SPIRIT</ab>
        <ab>BE YE ALSO READY</ab>
